data.text:
Print of an oil painting painted of Milne House, Westminster School in June 2023

Image size 30cm x 30cm

Image with border size 40cm x 40cm

Printed on the highest quality 150gsm German etching Hahnemühle paper.

Image is exactly the same size as the original painting with a 5cm border all round to fit a standard 40cm x 40cm frame
